(17, 'tt4197134', '2', 'Chosen: Part 1', 'MV5BMTQ2NjA3OTg3Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzkwNTAzNzE@', 'Princess Amberle Elessedil is selected to be a member of the Chosen that cares for the most sacred Elven tree, the Ellcrys. However she is given a vision of the Ellcrys dying, which could mean trouble for the Four Lands.', 1, 1, '5 Jan. 2016'),
