(204, 'tt4138324', '6', 'The Nuclear Man', 'MV5BMjIwNTQ4NzY3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjU4NTM0NDE@', 'After Ronnie attacks a physicist, Barry and the team go after him. Joe enlists Cisco''s help in the reinvestigation of Nora Allen''s murder. Barry struggles with his relationship and his duties as The Flash.', 1, 13, '10 Feb. 2015'),
