(206, 'tt4138338', '6', 'Out of Time', 'MV5BMTU5Nzk5MzQxN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTc0NDM4NDE@', 'Mark Mardon, having survived his apparent death during the black-matter explosion, returns seeking revenge on Joe for the death of his brother Clyde and has the same weather-manipulation powers as his deceased sibling.', 1, 15, '17 Mar. 2015'),
(207, 'tt4138340', '6', 'Rogue Time', 'MV5BMTk0NTYyMDg1OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzY3NDM4NDE@', 'The Flash learns that Captain Cold and Heat Wave have returned to Central City. This time Snart has brought along his baby sister Lisa aka Golden Glider to help wreak havoc on the city.', 1, 16, '24 Mar. 2015'),
(208, 'tt4138344', '6', 'Tricksters', 'MV5BMTgxNDE2NTAyNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDc3MTExNTE@', 'A copy-cat-killer who goes by the name The Trickster starts setting off bombs in Central City. In order to stop the villain, Barry and Joe meet with the original Trickster, a criminal mastermind named James Jesse, who has been imprisoned for 20 years. Thi', 1, 17, '31 Mar. 2015'),
(209, 'tt4138352', '6', 'All Star Team Up', 'MV5BMTQ5NDY1Mzk5Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODExOTgzNTE@', 'Felicity Smoak and Ray come to Central City seeking help with Ray''s suit; a meta-human releases deadly robotic bees; a group dinner does not go as planned.', 1, 18, '14 Apr. 2015'),
(210, 'tt4138350', '6', 'Who Is Harrison Wells?', 'MV5BMjAxMzA2MzAxMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTM1MzI0NTE@', 'Joe and Cisco visit Starling City and ask Captain Lance for help with their investigation into Dr. Wells; Laurel asks Cisco for a favor; Barry faces a new foe who can disguise himself into anyone he touches.', 1, 19, '21 Apr. 2015'),
(211, 'tt4138356', '6', 'The Trap', 'MV5BMjE5MTk4MTc3NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDA0OTA1NTE@', 'Barry, Caitlin, Cisco, and Joe set a trap for Wells. Cisco uses himself as bait which puts him in great danger. Meanwhile, Eddie makes a decision regarding Iris, which leaves Joe a bit unsettled.', 1, 20, '28 Apr. 2015'),
(212, 'tt4138376', '6', 'Grodd Lives', 'MV5BMTQzMTk3MzI3OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTg0OTA1NTE@', 'Barry deals with the latest threat from the Reverse-Flash; Dr. Wells distracts the team by releasing Grodd on the city; Iris and Barry have a serious talk.', 1, 21, '5 May 2015'),
(213, 'tt4138378', '6', 'Rogue Air', 'MV5BMTczNzE5NjU1Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTM4MzI2NTE@', 'Dr. Wells reactivates the particle accelerator and Barry has to move the Meta humans away. To do that, he needs help and he chooses to ask Captain Cold for it.', 1, 22, '12 May 2015'),
