(406, 'tt0751119', '10', 'F. Emasculata', 'MV5BMTUzODM4MTM3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTA0Nzc3MjE@', 'As Scully investigates the spread of a deadly contagion at a prison, Mulder tracks down two escaped convicts infected with the disease.', 2, 22, '28 Apr. 1995'),
(407, 'tt0751206', '10', 'Soft Light', 'MV5BNjQ3NDAxNTA4OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzU1Nzc3MjE@', 'The agents hunt down a scientist who is literally afraid of his own shadow.', 2, 23, '5 May 1995'),
(408, 'tt0751173', '10', 'Our Town', 'MV5BMjM0NjQ4MTUxM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjg0Nzc3MjE@', 'Reports of foxfire on a field in Dudley, Arkansas lead Mulder and Scully to a bizarre situation regarding the townsfolk. Employees of the Chaco Chicken Corporation are displaying bizarre behavior, and the death rate is slowly increasing.', 2, 24, '12 May 1995'),
