(903, 'tt1588681', '17', 'My Bloody Valentine', 'MV5BMjA3MjQwNDY5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMDQ4MTgxMw@@', 'A couple of days before Valentines Day, two valentines devour each other. On the next day, two lovers commit suicide. Dean and Sam investigate the murders and summon Castiel to help them. Castiel tells that the responsible is a cupid that has gone nuts. T', 5, 14, '11 Feb. 2010'),
