(1308, 'tt3381714', '21', 'Lord Baltimore (No. 104)', 'MV5BNDU4MzQ5OTQ4Ml5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzkxNTc0MjE@', 'Red continues to battle Berlin and faces a new threat from a man named Lord Baltimore. An important person comes back from the past into Red''s world. Meanwhile, Liz tries to move forward with her life after her showdown with Tom.', 2, 1, '22 Sep. 2014'),
