(1861, 'tt1017765', '27', 'Testing 1-2-3', 'MV5BMTQxNjg4NTEwMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTY3NDgzMjE@', 'The interns face their first year medical exams. With the interns busy, the attendings must do their own legwork, Burke appoints a new best man, Cristina writes her vows, and Callie grows suspicious of George and Izzie.', 3, 24, '10 May 2007'),
(1862, 'tt1020626', '27', 'Didn''t We Almost Have It All?', 'MV5BMTY0MjU4OTcxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDQ1NDczMjE@', 'The wedding day arrives. Richard chooses the new Chief and Chief Resident, the interns receive their exam results, Callie drops a bombshell on George while Izzie pours her heart out to him, and Burke makes an important decision.', 3, 25, '17 May 2007'),
