(1871, 'tt1002889', '27', 'Crash Into Me: Part 1', 'MV5BMTY0NTQyNTMyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTY1MzczMjE@', 'An accident in the ER bay leaves two paramedics fighting for their lives, and a third who refuses Bailey''s care. Meanwhile, Alex juggles two women, and Lexie begins to bond with a patient.', 4, 9, '22 Nov. 2007'),
(1872, 'tt1002869', '27', 'Crash Into Me: Part 2', 'MV5BMTQ3MjY3MjQ1M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDk0MzczMjE@', 'Tragedy abounds for everyone at Seattle Grace as they all continue in efforts to get the paramedic out of the overturned ambulance, stop the bleeding of a man who won''t quit, and a bigot with a Nazi tattoo on his stomach. On the personal side, Rebecca ret', 4, 10, '6 Dec. 2007'),
(1873, 'tt1002870', '27', 'Lay Your Hands on Me', 'MV5BNjMzNzA4MTkwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODI1MzczMjE@', 'Bailey''s son comes to the ER, Derek takes a housing step that puts pressure on Meredith, Izzie has a crisis of faith, and Cristina''s choice may change her course with Hahn.', 4, 11, '10 Jan. 2008'),
