(1878, 'tt1002875', '27', 'Freedom: Part 1', 'MV5BMTQ5ODU0MDQxOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzQ1MzczMjE@', 'A surgical team battles the clock as they try to save a boy encased in cement, Karev''s situation with an ever-disintegrating Ava brings back painful memories that interfere with his judgment, Derek and Meredith have one last chance at their clinical trial', 4, 16, '22 May 2008'),
