(2229, 'tt1615558', '32', 'Kafkaesque', 'MV5BMTc2NjA4OTYyMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjYxMDg5MjE@', 'Skyler hatches a plan as Hank''s hospital bills stack up. Meanwhile, Walt and Gus come to a better understanding as Jesse, looking for more independence, pursues a new opportunity.', 3, 9, '16 May 2010'),
(2230, 'tt1615550', '32', 'Fly', 'MV5BMTQ0MDczMDY4OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzYxMDg5MjE@', 'There is a fly loose in the lab. Walt and Jesse must do whatever they can to kill it before it contaminates the meth.', 3, 10, '23 May 2010'),
(2231, 'tt1615551', '32', 'Abiquiu', 'MV5BMTU5OTAxNTI3M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTYxMDg5MjE@', 'Skyler gets more involved in Walt''s business, much to his chagrin as Hank struggles with his recovery. Meanwhile, Jesse takes an active role in his new enterprise, leading him to a startling discovery.', 3, 11, '30 May 2010'),
(2232, 'tt1615552', '32', 'Half Measures', 'MV5BMTM2NzA0MTExMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjczOTQ1Mw@@', 'Against Walt''s advice, Jesse lashes out. Fearing for Jesse''s safety, Walt takes drastic action to intervene. Meanwhile a tragic event leads to a shocking confrontation.', 3, 12, '6 Jun. 2010'),
(2233, 'tt1615553', '32', 'Full Measure', 'MV5BMTM1Njc3OTkwOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwOTkyMDY1Mw@@', 'Jesse has disappeared and Walt is in big trouble with Gus. So Gus rehires Gale to learn from Walt''s cooking so that they can dispose of Walt once and for all.', 3, 13, '13 Jun. 2010'),
(2234, 'tt1683084', '32', 'Box Cutter', 'MV5BMTA2NzQzODA3OTdeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU3MDY3NjU2NzU@', 'Walt and Jesse are held captive for Gus, after Gale''s death. Meanwhile, Skyler tries to find out what happened to Walt.', 4, 1, '17 Jul. 2011'),
(2235, 'tt1683089', '32', 'Thirty-Eight Snub', 'MV5BMTQ4NTM1OTI1MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzg5OTc5MjE@', 'Walt attempts to form a new alliance as he plans his next move. Meanwhile Skyler pushes Walt towards a business opportunity, in hopes of protecting the family.', 4, 2, '24 Jul. 2011'),
(2236, 'tt1683090', '32', 'Open House', 'MV5BNzg1MTcxMDI2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjE1MDMxNg@@', 'While Walt worries about Gus''s interference and Jesse''s increasingly fragile state of mind, Skyler steps up the pressure to get what she wants.', 4, 3, '31 Jul. 2011'),
(2237, 'tt1683091', '32', 'Bullet Points', 'MV5BMTU2NzIyNjMyNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODc5OTc5MjE@', 'As Skyler concocts an elaborate story to explain the Whites'' finances, a worried Walt discovers that Hank has begun a new investigation.', 4, 4, '7 Aug. 2011'),
(2238, 'tt1683092', '32', 'Shotgun', 'MV5BMjE4NDM3MzkzMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjEzODcyNg@@', 'Jesse rides shotgun with Mike on a perilous run of pickups, prompting Walt to worry that his partner is about to be killed.', 4, 5, '14 Aug. 2011'),
(2239, 'tt1683093', '32', 'Cornered', 'MV5BMjE2NTQ1MDQ5MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTg5OTc5MjE@', 'Skyler adopts an aloof approach when she suspects that Walt isn''t telling her the truth. Meanwhile, Jesse proves his worth to Mike and Gus.', 4, 6, '21 Aug. 2011'),
(2240, 'tt1683094', '32', 'Problem Dog', 'MV5BMjMyODYwNDQ5M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDg5OTc5MjE@', 'Ordered to return the car he bought for his son, Walt strikes back by putting Skyler in a tough spot with their new money-laundering operation.', 4, 7, '28 Aug. 2011'),
