(2420, 'tt3251424', '36', 'Keaton', 'MV5BMTYxOTk0ODA4NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTc2NTc0MDE@', 'Jess throws a Halloween Party, but Cece won''t attend if Schmidt is there. In an effort to change Schmidt''s sullen behavior, Jess, Nick and Winston resort to pretending to be his childhood idol, Michael Keaton.', 3, 6, '22 Oct. 2013'),
(2421, 'tt3216958', '36', 'Coach', 'MV5BMTk3ODAyMzQ5OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTQ1NTU1MDE@', 'When Coach returns to town and takes the other guys to a strip club, an unhappy Jess retaliates by having a girls'' night out with Cece.', 3, 7, '5 Nov. 2013'),
(2422, 'tt3301670', '36', 'Menus', 'MV5BMTY2NjcyMjk3N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTAzMTIyMjE@', 'Coach tells Nick to give him a day to help change Nick''s life with diet and exercise. Jess takes action when menus for the same Chinese restaurant keep getting delivered to the loft.', 3, 8, '12 Nov. 2013'),
(2423, 'tt3295812', '36', 'Longest Night Ever', 'MV5BMjMxOTM0NTE2NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDQ3OTQ2MDE@', 'Jess is tasked with keeping a frantic Schmidt occupied as Coach and Cece go out on a date. Meanwhile, Nick and Winston meet a frisky bus driver as they search for a missing Ferguson.', 3, 9, '19 Nov. 2013'),
(2424, 'tt3352356', '36', 'Thanksgiving III', 'MV5BMTQyNzcxOTMxN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTAxNDc5MjE@', 'After Coach accuses him of going soft since he started dating Jess, Nick arranges a camping trip for the gang on Thanksgiving. Winston and Cece bond over their hatred of camping.', 3, 10, '26 Nov. 2013'),
