(2562, 'tt3460974', '38', 'More Bad Than Good', 'MV5BMjI0NjQzOTQyMV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzM3ODEzMjE@', 'Scott and his friends race to figure out how to catch the Werecoyote before it''s hunted down while Derek and Peter are broken out of captivity by an unlikely ally.', 3, 15, '13 Jan. 2014'),
