(2569, 'tt3460998', '38', 'The Fox and the Wolf', 'MV5BMzg2MjI4MDQ5M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDc3ODEzMjE@', 'While Allison, Derek, Chris and Sheriff Stilinski try to track down Nogitsune, Kira''s mother tells the story of the Nogitsune she came to know.', 3, 22, '3 Mar. 2014'),
