(2617, 'tt1976882', '39', 'Inside Track', 'MV5BMTQ3Nzg5OTM4MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODY4OTUyMjE@', 'Harvey asks Mike to find a loophole so that he can oust the incoming CEO of a motor company he represents, while Louis puts outrageous demands on Mike as he tries to make arrangements for the Rookie Dinner.', 1, 3, '7 Jul. 2011'),
