(2626, 'tt2014019', '39', 'Dog Fight', 'MV5BMTQwODM1NzgxN15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjY3MjUyMjE@', 'In the first-season finale, Harvey tries to free an innocent man,Clifford Danner (Neil Brown Jr.), but hits a wall when he goes to the district attorney (Chi McBride), who seems more focused on preserving the system than seeking justice. Elsewhere, Trevor', 1, 12, '8 Sep. 2011'),
(2627, 'tt2185442', '39', 'She Knows', 'MV5BMTQxODA5OTk1Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDI0MjUyMjE@', 'When Jessica learns about Mike, she tells Harvey, thinking that he doesn''t know, and tells him to fire him. But Harvey tries to stall hoping to find a way not to. And when Daniel Hardman, the Hardman in Pearson Hardman, decides to return to the firm, Jess', 2, 1, '14 Jun. 2012'),
(2628, 'tt2397283', '39', 'The Choice', 'MV5BMjI3ODE0NjM2OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzQzMDM5Nw@@', 'With Hardman back and knowing that it''s a matter of time before he challenges Jessica for control. She decides to make sure she has enough support. So she asks Harvey to go out and get it. Problem is that he rubbed so many members of the firm the wrong wa', 2, 2, '21 Jun. 2012'),
(2629, 'tt2199752', '39', 'Meet the New Boss', 'MV5BMTAyNTAzMjgzNDVeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU4MDI4MTM2MjIx', 'When Hardman comes in, he tries to ingratiate himself by asking Jessica to let him handle a case wherein they''re trying to keep some nurses from going on strike by negotiating a contract. But Jessica says that she already gave it to Harvey which was a lie', 2, 3, '28 Jun. 2012'),
(2630, 'tt2199756', '39', 'Discovery', 'MV5BMTU1Njk4OTk1OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjYxMzYyMjE@', 'Travis Tanner returns and he is suing a client of Harvey''s and Harvey claiming they deliberately withheld information and slandered someone. Harvey claims he did nothing but Tanner shows him a document which Harvey claims he never saw. So Harvey tries to ', 2, 4, '12 Jul. 2012'),
(2631, 'tt2253942', '39', 'Break Point', 'MV5BMTA5OTQ2MzYwMzNeQTJeQWpwZ15BbWU3MDE0MjgxMTg@', 'Harvey balks when Jessica puts him in the passenger seat on a lawsuit that could make or break the firm, and his back seat driving may have far reaching consequences. Mike takes the lead on a case that pits a tennis phenom against his trainer who also hap', 2, 5, '19 Jul. 2012'),
(2632, 'tt2199758', '39', 'All In', 'MV5BMjIxMzY2Njc1Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjYyODExOA@@', 'Harvey''s personal history with a client forces he and Mike to take on an unorthodox case from which they''d normally walk away. Louis and Rachel team up to save a mutually beloved institution from ruin. Jessica runs into an unexpected roadblock while defen', 2, 6, '26 Jul. 2012'),
(2633, 'tt2268628', '39', 'Sucker Punch', 'MV5BMjE4OTgxNjU0OV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMTEyNTAyOA@@', 'As the fallout continues to reverberate from the pending lawsuit against Pearson Hardman, Harvey turns to a former colleague, with whom he has a thorny past, for help in proving the firm''s case.', 2, 7, '2 Aug. 2012'),
(2634, 'tt2305044', '39', 'Rewind', 'MV5BMTQwMzg1NjkwNV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMjcxNTAyOA@@', 'With the vote for managing partner approaching, Harvey decides to take off but before leaving he gives Mike an assignment. We then take a look at of how things were 5 years ago; Harvey is an associate and Hardman was still managing partner and Jessica lea', 2, 8, '9 Aug. 2012'),
(2635, 'tt2310538', '39', 'Asterisk', 'MV5BMjAyNzIxODQ5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwNjcxNTAyOA@@', 'Harvey and Jessica get ready for the vote. They learn that the vote is split after Hardman got rid of one of Jessica''s supporters and that Hardman made Louis a Senior Partner and as a result is the deciding vote. Jessica wants Harvey to get him to vote fo', 2, 9, '16 Aug. 2012'),
