(2960, 'tt3233526', '43', 'Pilot', 'MV5BMTkyODc3NTE5Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODA2NDk3MzE@', 'Sex, drugs and classical music illustrate what happens behind the curtains at the symphony can be just as captivating as what occurs on stage.', 1, 1, '6 Feb. 2014'),
(2961, 'tt4157180', '43', 'Fifth Chair', 'MV5BMTQzODQ4NDg5OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTIzMDI4MzE@', 'Inspired by Hailey''s passion, Rodrigo insists that she play with the orchestra, over the objections of Gloria (Bernadette Peters). Veteran maestro Thomas (Malcolm McDowell) tries to rise above his resentment of Rodrigo, only to face more humiliations. Hai', 1, 2, '23 Dec. 2014'),
(2962, 'tt4170016', '43', 'Silent Symphony', 'MV5BNjQ3MjU4NjEyNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODIzMDI4MzE@', 'Alex helps Hailey figure out an easy way to make money, while back at the symphony hall, an older musician collapses when Rodrigo pushes him too hard. After being humiliated by Rodrigo''s assistant, Hailey lets off a lifetime of steam, and is caught off gu', 1, 3, '23 Dec. 2014'),
(2963, 'tt4170020', '43', 'You Have Insulted Tchaikovsky', 'MV5BMTQ5NzY5MDU2NV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNjIzMDI4MzE@', 'Gloria hosts a fundraiser to introduce Rodrigo. Hailey is sent to retrieve him and Thomas steps in to perform. When Rodrigo finally arrives to wow the crowd, Thomas can no longer contain himself. But the new maestro isn''t enjoying himself -- he''s haunted ', 1, 4, '23 Dec. 2014'),
(2964, 'tt4062368', '43', 'I''m with the Maestro', 'MV5BNjE2ODU5Nzg5NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzIzMDI4MzE@', 'Rodrigo seeks guidance to rid himself of his "dreadful passion." With Thomas gone on a sabbatical, Cynthia bonds with Betty. In the middle of Alex''s showcase -- an intimate dance with his roommate -- Hailey is summoned by Rodrigo to keep him from seeing A', 1, 5, '23 Dec. 2014'),
(2965, 'tt4170024', '43', 'The Rehearsal', 'MV5BMzgwMjQ5NDM5Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTIzMDI4MzE@', 'As pressure mounts before the launch of the new season, Rodrigo erupts. His behavior alarms the symphony''s business advisor, Edward, who warns Gloria to rein him in - just as her star conductor takes the orchestra on a surprise field trip. In the wake of ', 1, 6, '23 Dec. 2014'),
(2966, 'tt4170028', '43', 'You Go to My Head', 'MV5BMTc5MDM1NTA5N15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDMzMDI4MzE@', 'At a fundraising gala at an estate, Edward offers a large sum if Rodrigo will play the violin. Rodrigo ups the ante and turns the tables. Hailey runs into Lizzie, and discovers her roommate has been hiding her upper crust roots -- before spending the rest', 1, 7, '23 Dec. 2014'),
(2967, 'tt4170030', '43', 'Mozart with the Bacon', 'MV5BMjMyMDAzMjg3Nl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDIzMDI4MzE@', 'When Rodrigo decides he doesn''t want Winslow Elliot for his opening night, the legendary pianist confronts him, and ends up helping him realize who he does want. Cynthia is sent to track down Thomas, but isn''t quite prepared for what greets her. Hailey gi', 1, 8, '23 Dec. 2014'),
(2968, 'tt4170032', '43', 'Now, Fortissimo!', 'MV5BNjAzODg5MTIyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzIzMDI4MzE@', 'Rodrigo summons Hailey to drive him upstate to find Ana Maria, explaining that she "makes him alive," exactly what the symphony needs opening night. Back in the city, Cynthia takes some pills for her wrist, and ends up seeing a co-worker in a whole new li', 1, 9, '23 Dec. 2014'),
(2969, 'tt4170036', '43', 'Opening Night', 'MV5BMjU0OTkwODQyM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjIzMDI4MzE@', 'After a harsh verdict from Betty, Hailey is ready to give up on her dream. But as the crowd fills the hall for opening night, Betty has gone missing. No one in the orchestra is prepared for what happens next. As their tempestuous new soloist, Ana Maria, g', 1, 10, '23 Dec. 2014'),
(2970, 'tt4461048', '43', 'Stern Papa', 'MV5BODczNTMzNDAzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTk0MDk1NzE@', 'The New York Symphony Orchestra is midway through their season and on the surface things are going well: audiences are happy and the musicians are playing better than ever. But offstage, things are beginning to unravel.', 2, 1, '30 Dec. 2015'),
(2971, 'tt5152502', '43', 'Nothing Resonates Like Rhinoceros Foreskin', 'MV5BNzA3NzUzMzAwM15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMTg0MDk1NzE@', 'A near disaster during a live performance forces Rodrigo to make some changes in how he conducts not only himself, but his orchestra. Gloria extends an unusual invitation to Hailey. But, as the young oboist will soon find out, there is no such thing as fr', 2, 2, '30 Dec. 2015'),
(2972, 'tt5242724', '43', 'It All Depends on You', 'MV5BNzg2NjUwOTkwNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNzg0MDk1NzE@', 'After one drum circle too many, Rodrigo is evicted from his apartment -- though it doesn''t take him long to find a new roommate. Hailey and Lizzie help Bradford record his podcast about a famed building for artists. Hailey thinks about her future as one o', 2, 3, '30 Dec. 2015'),
(2973, 'tt5242728', '43', 'Touché Maestro, Touché', 'MV5BMTU4Njg2NzQwOF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMjk0MDk1NzE@', 'Guest cellist, Andrew Walsh (Dermot Mulroney) invites Hailey out to see Lang Lang play, and gives her, her first real glimpse inside the world of classical music''s elite crew. Thomas and Rodrigo enjoy a rare guys night in and end up in a tent in a living ', 2, 4, '30 Dec. 2015'),
(2974, 'tt5242722', '43', 'Regresso Del Rey', 'MV5BMTY0MjcyMTY2MV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDg0MDk1NzE@', 'Hailey has more work than she planned on during the orchestra''s Latin American tour. When a stolen violin threatens the tour''s final concert in front of Rodrigo''s former maestro and a potential major donor, Rodrigo has to call in an old friend. An adventu', 2, 5, '30 Dec. 2015'),
(2975, 'tt5242726', '43', 'How to Make God Laugh', 'MV5BMTUzMzA1NzkxMl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwOTc0MDk1NzE@', 'Rodrigo shows Hailey HIS Mexico and takes her to a performance of his childhood youth orchestra. Thomas and Gloria meet with Juan Luis Delgado, the richest man in Mexico. Cynthia gets a surprise visitor and ends up in an unexpected position. Maestro River', 2, 6, '30 Dec. 2015'),
(2976, 'tt5108698', '43', 'Can You Marry a Moon?', 'MV5BMTUzMzIxMjIzMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzg0MDk1NzE@', 'The gang celebrates Betty''s 35 years in the orchestra with some tequila and a special guest. Hailey breaks the cardinal rule of touring: what happens on the road, stays on the road. Negotiations hit a wall and the idea of a work stoppage begins to sink in', 2, 7, '30 Dec. 2015'),
(2977, 'tt5242730', '43', 'Leave Everything Behind', 'MV5BNTMxODIwMDE0MF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDk0MDk1NzE@', 'Thomas shares his symphony with soon-to-be-ex-wife Claire, who finds the music absolutely breathtaking. A funeral becomes the setting of backstage plotting between the orchestra and the board. Rodrigo attempts to let go of something from his past, but she', 2, 8, '30 Dec. 2015'),
(2978, 'tt5052426', '43', 'Amusia', 'MV5BMjA0NzA5ODk4M15BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNDk0MDk1NzE@', 'Lennox, a guest "enfant terrible" conductor, brings some anger and fury to the orchestra. Thomas battles his oldest demons and hears the crash of his legacy. Rodrigo does everything in his power to keep the world around him from going out of tune. Nina an', 2, 9, '30 Dec. 2015'),
(2979, 'tt5085672', '43', 'Home', 'MV5BMTc4OTkzNTg3NF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODc0MDk1NzE@', 'Things are about to erupt between the board and the orchestra, and Rodrigo prepares to do whatever it takes. As the tables turn with each double cross, no one is safe. Not even the greatest composers in history. The future is uncertain.', 2, 10, '30 Dec. 2015'),
(2980, 'tt3591824', '44', 'Descenso', 'MV5BMTY3MTIxODMzMF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwODgyMzk2NjE@', 'Chilean drug chemist Cockroach brings his product to Colombian smuggler Pablo Escobar. DEA agent Steve Murphy joins the war on drugs in Bogota.', 1, 1, '28 Aug. 2015'),
(2981, 'tt3736868', '44', 'The Sword of Simón Bolivar', '01', 'Communist radical group M-19 makes a move against the narcos, while Murphy gets an education in Colombian law enforcement from his new partner Peña.', 1, 2, '28 Aug. 2015'),
(2982, 'tt3736866', '44', 'The Men of Always', 'MV5BMjQzODQ0NDMzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTEzMzk2NjE@', 'Murphy encounters the depths of government corruption when he and Peña try to derail Escobar''s political ambitions by proving he''s a narco.', 1, 3, '28 Aug. 2015'),
(2983, 'tt3736870', '44', 'The Palace in Flames', '01', 'Despite a new extradition treaty, the U.S. puts more money into fighting communism, creating new challenges for Murphy and Peña in the hunt for Pablo.', 1, 4, '28 Aug. 2015'),
(2984, 'tt3736874', '44', 'There Will Be a Future', 'MV5BNTExNzM2MzYxNl5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMDMzMzk2NjE@', 'Pablo''s extreme methods put the narcos on the brink of war with Carillo and the government. Peña tries to protect his witness.', 1, 5, '28 Aug. 2015'),
(2985, 'tt3736872', '44', 'Explosivos', 'MV5BMjIyMjc1MzQ0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwNTM4NDcyNjE@', 'Peña and Carillo close in on Gacha. Murphy tries to protect pro-extradition candidate Gaviria from a notorious assassin connected to Pablo.', 1, 6, '28 Aug. 2015'),
(2986, 'tt3736876', '44', 'You Will Cry Tears of Blood', '01', 'Pablo goes into hiding as the political tide turns against him, but he finds a way to strike back. Murphy and Peña finally get the CIA to help them.', 1, 7, '28 Aug. 2015'),
(2987, 'tt3736878', '44', 'La Gran Mentira', '01', 'A tragic mistake forces the government to change tactics in the fight against Pablo. But Pablo faces bigger threats from inside his empire.', 1, 8, '28 Aug. 2015'),
(2988, 'tt3736882', '44', 'La Catedral', '01', 'The hunt for Pablo seems to be over after he makes a deal with the government, but Murphy and Peña - and the Cali Cartel - have other plans.', 1, 9, '28 Aug. 2015'),
